ce Plateau |[[International Polar Year|IPY]] LARISSA |{{Coord|66|2||S|64|4||W}} |1976 |2010 |143 |<ref>Zagorodnov et al. (2012), p. 675.</ref> |- |Bruce Plateau |[[International Polar Year|IPY]] LARISSA |{{Coord|66|2||S|64|4||W}} |1976 |2010 |448 |<ref>Goodwin et al. (2016), p. 2582.</ref><ref>Goodwin et al. (2016), p. 2593.</ref> |}
