-2012.pdf|journal=The Cryosphere|volume=6|pages=675–686|via=|date=|last2=Nagornov|first2=O.|last3=Scambos|first3=T.A.|last4=Muto|first4=A.|last5=Mosley-Thompson|first5=E.|last6=Pettit|first6=E.C.|last7=Tyuflin|first7=S.|doi=10.5194/tc-6-675-2012}}
